{"tid":768054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【盧凱彤墮斃】fb三日前最後發文：今天準備去做一件大事","createTime":"2018-08-05T05:26:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T06:17:57.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"80c33b33d2a58a6de0a5918cff1da57e768363e8","tid":768054,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T05:26:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180805/large/1533444828_7302.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180805%2Flarge%2F1533444828_7302.jpg&h=1e669b4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港樂隊at17的32歲女歌手盧凱彤（Ellen）今晨在跑馬地墮樓身亡。她在社交平台最後一則發文為大前日(2日)中午，她附上自拍照指：「今天準備去做一件大事，是我踏入三字頭以來其中一件為自己做主的事，我很看重，也為自己訂下一個新目標，終於明白點解d人咁鐘意自拍，因為士氣高漲時真的會想幫自己留倩影」。<br />\n<br />\n文章後加注hashtag「劉善映」(留倩影)、「妄想症候群」、「其實只不過約咗人飲茶」、「化行妝去搭地鐵」、「大事發生前」，從自拍照中可見，盧凱彤短髮整潔、妝容簡潔，正在喝飲料。<br />\n消息傳出短短約1小時，有逾1,100人在文章下留言悼念。"},{"pid":"0fa707a1da4ac3df34c532c0f0a39ec203953535","tid":768054,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T05:29:52.000Z","msg":"香港新聞好撚煩 <br />\n成日放大番人地以前d相同表情黎分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b1c8e1dff92fde7f7851ff32e2bca0abffbd729","tid":768054,"uid":35014,"like":2,"dislike":33,"score":-31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T05:30:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e1a3ef2acf65ee66e0d6a708e5e0bad965fa942","tid":768054,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T05:32:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40d37fb3fedc796220f2275b323c3023de18fb11","tid":768054,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T05:32:02.000Z","msg":"如果件大事係去跳樓就應該三日前就跳，分分鐘其實係畀人謀殺"},{"pid":"fc8fedd91d4dd927ad72db66370ea0620a286c7c","tid"